data.description: Open House October 28th 2023  100% Financing With USDA! $5,000 towards Painting/Flooring/ Closing Cost. Welcome to this stunning 4-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom home situated on a spacious 3-acre lot. As you approach the property, you'll be greeted by a large rocking chair front porch, perfect for enjoying your morning coffee while listening to the birds chirp. This home boasts 3 stories, with the master bedroom conveniently located on the main floor. Upstairs, you'll find two additional bedrooms that share a bathroom, along with a bonus room that can be used as a playroom, office, or additional living space. The basement of this home is a true gem, featuring an in-law suite with a separate entrance. This suite includes a mudroom, kitchen, gym space, dining area, and bathroom, providing the perfect space for extended family or guests. The master bedroom showcases trey ceilings and a double vanity in the ensuite bathroom with tiled shower and separate bath creating a luxurious retreat for the owner. The kitchen is tiled and offers a large island, tons of cabinet space so its perfect for preparing meals and feeding the entire family. Step outside into the backyard where you will find an entertainment paradise with a oversize deck and patio area which is ideal for hosting gatherings and enjoying outdoor dining. The backyard also features an in-ground saltwater pool with a poolside bar equipped with a kegerator perfect for serving drinks to everyone for the family gatherings. For added convenience, there is a 430 square foot storage building, providing ample space for all of your storage needs. Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this incredible home with its desirable features and amenities. Schedule a showing today and make this your dream home! Seller is Motivated and would love to move this one fast. $1500 lender credit With approved lender Kyle Cameron with Fairway Independent Mortgage.678-850-0331
